freesmartphone.org Framework DBus Interface Specification

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Sources

Description

Pim Sources can be use to access a set of PIM data sources

Namespace

org.freesmartphone.PIM.Sources

Methods

  • Add
  • Query

Signals

None

Errors

None

Methods

Add ( a{sv} ) → s

Description: Add a contact into the default backend source.

Parameters

a{sv}: contact_data

contacts fields

Returns

s: path

Path of the newly created d-bus contact object

Query ( a{sv} ) → s

Description: Create a new Call to a given number, with an optional protocol.

Parameters

a{sv}: query

contacts fields that are queried

Returns

s: protocol

Path to the query object
